data.description: Welcome home to this charming three-bedroom, two-bath residence that welcomes you with open arms. Positioned ideally between Hurlburt and Eglin AFB, and a short drive away from our pristine sandy beaches, this home offers the perfect location. The heart of this home lies in the open connection between the kitchen, dining room, and living room. The Kitchen has beautiful quartz countertops, complemented by an abundance of natural lighting through the picture windows in the dining area, creating an inviting atmosphere. The three generously sized bedrooms offer ample space, with the master bedroom even featuring elegant French doors that lead to a private patio. Step into the backyard, where a patio awaits your outdoor gatherings and relaxation.
